data.description: Welcome to this single-story gem, blending daily comfort with unique opportunity. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.25 baths, and a recently updated kitchen, the home exudes modern charm. Situated on a spacious corner lot with a fully fenced yard and RV parking with power, with privacy and functionality. A standout feature is the garage, which is currently converted into a salon, waiting for your ideas or personal touches. The covered patio offers a tranquil outdoor space, ideal for relaxation or hosting. Centrally located between Seattle and Portland and minutes from Centralia and Chehalis shopping, this property marries convenience with potential. Explore, envision, and make it yours.
